ations and appears more robust with respect to\ncross-talk than the least-squares shot-stacking.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 22 Jul 2019 07:28:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 3 Aug 2019 05:45:51 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 26 May 2020 16:17:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-10"}
