inner.\nHowever, the comparative evaluation also highlights the relative strengths of\ndifferent algorithms with respect to the type of performance criteria, e.g.,\nsocial welfare vs. attainment of equilibrium.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 22 Jul 2019 09:01:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-23"}
